On behalf of Charter Hall, CBRE is pleased to present Minto Logistics Hub to market for pre-lease. 

Minto Logistics Hub offers an exciting opportunity to secure a modern high clearance warehouse and logistics facilities with flexible tenancies available from 7,000-19,405sqm. Located in the heart of the Industrial hub of Minto, immediately west of the Southern Sydney Freight Line, the site offers superior access to major arterial motorways with convenient access to the Hume Highway and M5 and M7 Motorways. 

Building Features:
- Warehouse 1: 20m wide awning, 30-55m hardstand
- Warehouse 2: 36m super awning, 36m hardstand
- Minimum 10.5m springing height 
- Ridge height 13.7m 
- Sunken and on-grade dock access available 
- ESFR fire suppression system 
- Separate car and truck access at each tenancy 
- Fronting Southern Sydney Freight Line 

For further information please contact exclusive agents at CBRE.

On behalf of Charter Hall, CBRE is pleased to bring Minto Logistics Hub to market for lease.

Minto Logistics Hub offers a rare opportunity to secure quality hail netted hardstand in the highly sought-after and well-connected Minto area. Strategically located on both sides of Culverston Road, immediately west of the Southern Sydney Freight Line, the site provides convenient access to the Hume Highway, M5 Motorway and M7 Motorway, connecting with Sydney’s wider interconnected freeway network. 

Features: 
- 68,692sqm of hardstand/yard with office and amenity available now!
- Hail netted yard available.
- Hume Motorway only 1km from site. 
- M5 and M7 15kms from site.
- Access to all arterial roadways and Sydney’s interconnected freeway network.
- Flexibility around area requirements.
- Opportunity to develop tailored warehouse solutions.

For further information please contact the exclusively listed agents at CBRE.
